title: Post in this thread and I'll associate you with a Youtuber
body:
Basically title.

A few disclaimers, as I *know* jimmies will be rustled. =P

1. I don't know every Youtuber out there, just a few dozen. If you don't get matched "correctly" because I don't know the Youtuber, too bad.
2. I know you all (mostly) as just text and an avatar over the internet. I'll just associate you based on how I perceive you. 
3. If I don't know you personally, I'll likely be very inaccurate, lol.

Can't think of anymore for now. Brb for a few, I'll come back and start replying!
